<segment id="20" parent="1020" relname="joint">and the monkeys are screaming</segment>
<segment id="21" parent="1020" relname="joint">and they are holding their arms behind their backs .</segment>
<segment id="22" parent="1022" relname="span">The universities</segment>
<segment id="23" parent="1023" relname="span">who have grants from the federal government for animal research for the sheer reason</segment>
<segment id="24" parent="1024" relname="joint">that they want money for their football team and money for their President ’s flowers in the office ,</segment>
<segment id="25" parent="26" relname="attribution">they will not examine</segment>
